description:
I've been gone so long it feels weird to even be typing a description..

Anyway, sorry if the video was too talky -- there was so much to say, so many ways to say it, and I just wasn't sure how to. When it's all said and done though, I just wanted to say sorry that I left you all for so long without a word. Without any notice. I needed time away, which there is nothing wrong with, but I didn't let the Samurai know, and that's where I messed up.

I also apologized to my YouTube friends and fellow content creators that felt backlash from my sudden absence. Honestly, I didn't know that would be a repercussion of my leaving. So I'm sorry for the negative ways that affected you all.

I know I've said it before, but if ever there is a time in the future that a similar feeling starts to develop within me that I need to leave for a while, I WILL be letting you know. It's something that I struggle with -- ironically enough I feel like an update like that would be letting a lot of people down, but then NOT saying anything at all is of course letting a lot of people down, most likely more.

So once again, I'm sorry to everyone I let worry, and to everyone I let down. I've got a lot of making up for time to do, so for now I take my leave. I love you all so much. #LongLiveTheSamurai
